### Ask a question (preferred: send "question")
POST http://localhost:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the duty cycle?"
}

### Ask a question (back-compat: send both keys)
POST http://localhost:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "What is the duty cycle?",
  "question": "What is the duty cycle?"
}

### Contact escalation (unchanged)
POST http://localhost:8000/contact
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "reason": "user_clicked_contact",
  "transcript": [
    "Q: Example question",
    "A: Placeholder answer"
  ]
}
